Our campus-like setting with graceful Georgian architecture, quaint cobblestone footpaths, and endless natural beauty provides a stunning outdoor wedding space in Columbus for ceremonies, receptions and photography. Our professional wedding staff can help to transform any of our lovely outdoor spaces into an unforgettable scene.

  • Tranquil poolside patio overlooking a serene pondperfect for relaxed gatherings or sunset cocktails 
  • Brick-paved terrace framed by stunning arched, floor-to-ceiling windows that blend indoor elegance with outdoor charm 
  • Lush, manicured lawns shaded by mature trees and accented with vibrant seasonal landscaping 
  • Elegant white pergola adorned with cascading wisteria vines, creating a romantic and picturesque setting

The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center offers a variety of indoor and outdoor spaces for groups of every size, and our professional event planners will handle every detail so you can enjoy every minute. After a full day of learning, collaborating, and connecting, attendees will appreciate the comfort and convenience of our onsite hotelfeaturing 193 upscale guest rooms and suites just steps from the event spaces

No matter the occasion, The Ohioan is an experience your guests will never forget. When we say, \"All we do is everything\", we mean it! We've hosted a Pig Roast, Mardi Gras parties, A Night in Paris, Fall Harvest Gala, OSU Tailgates and countless other themed events.

Each package offers added convenience, curated amenities, and access to exclusive perks that make your stay more rewarding. 
Choose from a variety of options tailored to your needs, including packages that pair upscale accommodations with local attractions, business-friendly features, or family-focused experiences. Check-In / Check-Out   

Check-In Time: Starting at 3:00 pm

Check-Out Time: 12:00 pm

Minimum Age to Register: 21

Early Departure Fee

Early departure policy may vary depending on your reservation details. Please refer to your reservation confirmation to verify your early departure policy.

Late Check-Out Fee

Late check-out until 1:00 PM, based on availability. Late check-out after 1:00 PM will be subjected to a fee.

Cancellations   

Cancellation policies may vary depending on the rate or dates of your reservation. Please refer to your reservation confirmation to verify your cancellation policy. If you need further assistance, call the hotel at 614-880-4300.

Pets

Service animals allowed?  Yes

Pets allowed? Yes

Parking

Complimentary self-parking

Smoking

The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center is a smoke and tobacco-free facility. Smoking is permitted in designated areas. All Guest Rooms including balconies, are non-smoking.

In compliance with Ohio state law, smoking is prohibited in all guest rooms (including the room balconies) and buildings throughout the Ohioan Hotel & Event Center campus. There are two designated smoking areas: just south of the outdoor pool and on the far-north side of the Virginia building. Vapes and e-cigarettes are also prohibited in the rooms. Failure to comply will result in a $250 cleaning fee.

Stepping onto the secluded and park-like grounds of the Ohioan can feel like youre worlds away from the hustle and bustle of a city, yet our Columbus hotel is close to a number of exciting attractions! As Ohios capital city, there are always tons of things to do and our hotel and conference center provides guests with a luxurious stay close to the action.

With our hotels prime location near the John Glenn Columbus Airport, guests from all over visit The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center to enjoy an elegant stay near Columbus.

Upscale comfort, thoughtfully designed, The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center features 193 beautifully appointed guest rooms and suites that blend residential-style comfort with the elevated experience of an upscale boutique stay. Each room is curated with the modern traveler in mindwhether you're here for a conference, retreat, social event, or extended business stay. 


Enjoy complimentary high-speed wireless internet, VOIP telephones with speakerphone and voicemail, pillow-top mattresses, a full-length mirror, in-room refrigerators, and a premium in-room coffee experience, with upscale European bath amenities by TempleSpa. In addition, all rooms have our state-of-the-art audio-visual technology, which allows you to hook up your devices to our flat panel TVs. With a variety of room and suite options available, you can choose accommodations tailored to your preferencesensuring a restful stay just steps from your meeting or event.

A Hospitality Experience Like No Other","consider-as-h1[]":["Yes"],"snippet-description":"

When we acquired the Lewis Center property in the 1950s, it was situated in a remote, underdeveloped region.

Fast forward to today, and the property is a vibrant hub of progress and development. The site has become an anchor point in a thriving community growing better and more dynamic each year.

What began as a radio station in the 40s evolved into Green Meadows Inn during the 60s, which later transformed into a training center for Nationwide Insurance agents in the 70s, and ultimately expanded into a full-scale conference and hotel by the early 00s.

","snippet-description-more":"

As the region continues to grow, were committed to providing a premier destination for families, businesses, and communities to come together to connect, celebrate, build partnerships, and make memories that will last a lifetime.

As is typical in the life cycle of all great hotels and event facilities, it was time for a comprehensive renovation and rebranding. We took the opportunity to reimagine our property for the authentic Ohioan.

We are excited to renovate this historic property, preserving its rich character while introducing modern features that enhance both its beauty and functionality. By maintaining its integrity and authenticity, we are building upon an already vibrant property to create a space that is both timeless and forward-thinking.

The Ohioan is an anchor in our great state the elevated event center offers a reputation of rich history and stately appeal that is reflective of the property itself.

At The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center, our highest priority is delivering an exceptional meeting experienceevery guest, every industry, every time. Whether you're hosting a strategic planning session, leadership retreat, training seminar, or team-building event, our Columbus venue is designed to support productivity and innovation. 
 

With 35 flexible conference and breakout rooms, our meeting spaces feature ergonomic furnishings, non-glare tabletops, tackable and writable wall surfaces, adjustable lighting, and individual climate controlsensuring comfort and focus throughout the day.

Guests of The Ohioan Hotel & Event Center can indulge in a delicious 5-star breakfast without ever leaving the property! Each morning, wake up and head down to The Ohio Dining Room, our world-class on-site restaurant. Open for breakfast, it serves classic American cuisine in a beautiful setting overlooking the hotels sprawling grounds. Guests who book our Bed and Breakfast Package enjoy this decadent buffet as part of their overnight stay experience.

After a day of exploring, unwind at our inviting pub, featuring a variety of craft beers, cocktails, and flavorful pub fareperfect for relaxing evenings or casual gatherings. Whether starting your day or ending your night, our dining options offer something exceptional at The Ohioan.
